Definition: the state of being under the control of a force or influence or abstract power
Example: he was in bondage to fear; he sought release from his bondage to Satan; a self freed from the bondage of time
Synonyms: subjugation, the, state, of, being, under, control, a, force, or, influence, abstract, power, he, was, in, to, fear, sought, release, from, his, Satan, self, freed, time
Category: noun.state
